FASHION DESIGN

CREATIVE DIRECTION

As a designer, I represent women. I strive to challenge the stereotypes between fashion and humanity. Diversity and inclusivity drive my actions as a designer and encapsulate my brand's culture and identity.

With the construction of over twenty-five designs (and counting) for runways, I am able to express my interpretation and distinct understanding of fashion.

Behind every runway look is garment production, including sketching, designing, pattern drafting, sourcing materials, sewing, and styling. Showcasing includes organizing runway line ups, choreography, audio, and visuals. Constantly striving to create a lasting impression among audiences.

A special thank you to my runway teams consisting of models, hair stylists, make-up artists, and other industry professionals. Every moment I spend with you is a dream come true.
